-- Major changes in v2.0 of the Belacoin Wallet --

- Block explorer built into the wallet:  Searchable txID, block ID, hash, and addresses.
- Trade statistics of current exchanges trading BELA added and auto-updated every 60 seconds.
- Belacoin Pool statistics from pools currently mining BELA auto-updated every 60 seconds.
- Number of latest transactions displayed on the overview display changed to 6 from 3.
- Belacoin statistics including the current difficulty, blocks found, network hash rate and total BELA in circulation auto-updated every 60 seconds.
- Live news and alerts on the overview page to allow for emergency news, updates/upgrades, and other related events/news auto-updated every 60 seconds.
- New logo!

-- Minor general changes

- Majority of icons replaced
